    text: Press [E]<br>to inspect the trash can
    info: "\uD734\uC9C0\uD1B5 \uD504\uB86C\uD504\uD2B8 \uD14D\uC2A4\uD2B8"
  - id: Ptxt_KR_Object_13
    text: Press [E]<br>to inspect the toothbrush cup
    info: "\uCE6B\uC194 \uCEF5 \uD504\uB86C\uD504\uD2B8 \uD14D\uC2A4\uD2B8"
  - id: Ptxt_KR_Object_14
